Okay, how about this? You know
how at some point in the future,

344
00:17:41,682 --> 00:17:44,035
- machines will rise up against us?
- Sure.

345
00:17:44,160 --> 00:17:46,564
So, the machines...
they've killed everybody,

346
00:17:47,350 --> 00:17:48,475
