three days to call her.

361
00:18:30,485 --> 00:18:32,402
I knew where she worked,
so I tracked her down.

362
00:18:33,124 --> 00:18:35,047
Let me ask you.
Did I call you too soon?

363
00:18:35,172 --> 00:18:37,487
I loved that he called me
